---
title: Prawn Massaman Style Curry with Chickpeas, Green Beans and Rice
description: This Prawn Massaman Curry with Rice is bursting full of luxury flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prawn-massaman-style-curry-8b10826b-93273825.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/prawn-massaman-style-curry-5fc8ca3d582fdc41966b3839-24dafa2f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/prawn-massaman-style-curry-5fc8ca3d582fdc41966b3839
